<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.929.37666.figure12>
    dc:description "Figure 12. Genus Talahua Fluke: A head, frontal, male B basoflagellomere, frontal view C metacoxa pile tuft, ventral view D scutellum emarginated, dorsal view E male genitalia, lateral view F holotype, AMNH G paratype label, USNM. Scale bars: 5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/402766" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.929.37666.figure13>
    dc:description "Figure 13. Talahua fervida, male (CEUA 95345): A dorsal view, male B lateral view (Paratype USNM). Female (CEUA 93328): C lateral view D dorsal view E posterior view, detail of maculae on sixth tergum. Scale bars: 5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/402767" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.929.37666.figure14>
    dc:description "Figure 14. Talahua fervida, male genitalia: A whole genitalia including epandrium, cercus and surstylus, lateral view B hypandrium, dorsal view C cerci, and surstyli, ventral view D cerci and surstyli, dorsal view. Scale bar: 0.05 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/402768" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.929.37666.figure17>
